{
  "texts": [
    "In this paper, we will revisit some of the probes (specified in Sec.",
    "3.7) and check if the problems get alleviated in the LLM era.",
    "To our best knowledge, no previous work has comprehensively studied Video-LLMs' behavior in VideoQA.",
    "Several works explore specific phenomena with models from the stage of CNN/ViT+BERT.",
    "For example, (Buch et al., 2022) and (Lei et al., 2023) have revealed the single-frame bias issue, where a large number of questions can be answered with a single video frame."
  ]
}